<plot>Whilst travelling through the countryside, a young salaryman's journey is cut short when his car unexpectedly breaks down in the middle of nowhere. Stranded, alone, unsure what to do, he sees a figure in the distance resembling a woman. Foolishly he begins to follow her towards some woods, where he will find more than he expected.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?498907</url></doc>
